          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These filters are applied on top of the agent profile and determine which tools the runtime can actually call.": {
      "comment": "A footer text for the \"Tool Filters\" section of the AgentCapabilitiesView.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这些过滤器叠加在智能体配置档之上，并决定运行时实际可调用哪些工具。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These handoff signals are local to this iPhone and help keep operator follow-through visible inside the incident flow.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这些交接信号仅保存在这台 iPhone 上，用于在事故流中保持操作跟进可见。"
