            "value": "低速な支出、自動化、ルーティングの深掘りは主要導線の後ろに置きます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep the next operator exits compact and visible above the provider, channel, and drift inventory.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
